CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782181080
OL,3,CShoppers 'making 1.7bn high street
OL,4,Cvisits per year driven by social media'
OL,6,FSocial media is driving an estimated
OL,7,F1.7 billion visits to UK high streets
OL,8,Fannually ` an average of more than 30
OL,9,Fmillion visits a week ` analysis
OL,10,Fsuggests.
OL,12,FThe "hype to high street" study from
OL,13,FAmerican Express, carried out with
OL,14,Fanalysts Retail Economics, indicated
OL,15,Fthat nearly two-thirds (63%) of UK
OL,16,Fadults have visited a shop or
OL,17,Fhospitality venue within the past
OL,18,Fyear, such as a cafe or restaurant,
OL,19,Fafter being influenced by content they
OL,20,Fsaw on social media.
OL,26,@tD@EOUtD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
