OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782181080
OL,3,CShoppers 'making 1.7bn high street
OL,4,Cvisits per year driven by social media'
OL,6,FAmong Gen-Z shoppers aged 18 to 28,
OL,7,Fthe proportion rises to 88%.
OL,9,FThe research also indicated that such
OL,10,Fvisits can also lead to customer
OL,11,Floyalty.
OL,13,FMore than four-fifths (82%) of people
OL,14,Freturn to a business after a socially-
OL,15,Finfluenced first visit, rising to 96%
OL,16,Famong the Gen-Z age groups.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782181080
OL,3,CShoppers 'making 1.7bn high street
OL,4,Cvisits per year driven by social media'
OL,6,FThese customers also help to spread
OL,7,Fthe word about businesses online, with
OL,8,Fnearly four-fifths (79%) saying they
OL,9,Fshared their most recent visit in some
OL,10,Fway ` whether that meant recommending
OL,11,Fthat business, posting about it on
OL,12,Fsocial media or leaving a review
OL,13,Fonline.
OL,15,FAmong the Gen-Z age group, the
OL,16,Fproportion rises to 89%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782181080
OL,3,CShoppers 'making 1.7bn high street
OL,4,Cvisits per year driven by social media'
OL,6,FSocial media posts about products or
OL,7,Fstores are also prompting a "viral
OL,8,Fpilgrimage" economy, where consumers
OL,9,Ftravel significant distances to
OL,10,Fexperience products, venues and trends
OL,11,Fthey first discovered online, American
OL,12,FExpress said.
OL,14,FMore than a third (35%) of the Gen-Z
OL,15,Fage group surveyed have travelled to
OL,16,Fanother city or region to purchase a
OL,17,Fproduct they first saw trending online.
OL,26,@oD@]OUpD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
