OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782181080
OL,3,CShoppers 'making 1.7bn high street
OL,4,Cvisits per year driven by social media'
OL,6,FOnce there, nearly nine in 10 (87%)
OL,7,Fsaid they would be willing to queue
OL,8,Ffor a sought-after product or
OL,9,Fexperience.
OL,11,FThe research was based on a survey of
OL,12,F2,000 people across the UK in April,
OL,13,Fcombined with economic modelling to
OL,14,Festimate the total value and volume of
OL,15,Fsocial media-influenced spending on UK
OL,16,Fhigh streets.
OL,18,FSurvey responses were combined with
OL,19,Fretail and hospitality spending data.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782181080
OL,3,CShoppers 'making 1.7bn high street
OL,4,Cvisits per year driven by social media'
OL,6,FNearly nine in 10 (87%) people
OL,7,Freported spending money during a
OL,8,Fsocially influenced visit, rising to
OL,9,F94% among Gen-Z shoppers.
OL,11,FRetail Economics' modelling suggests
OL,12,Fthat social media now influences one
OL,13,Fin every 20 in-person high street
OL,14,Fpurchases across the UK.
OL,16,FThere is also a ripple effect for high
OL,17,Fstreets, with around a third (32%) of
OL,18,Fpeople saying they visited additional
OL,19,Fnearby shops, restaurants or venues
OL,20,Fduring a socially influenced trip.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782181080
OL,3,CShoppers 'making 1.7bn high street
OL,4,Cvisits per year driven by social media'
OL,6,FMore than a fifth (22%) of Gen-Z
OL,7,Fshoppers said they spent more than
OL,8,Foriginally planned once they arrived.
OL,10,FDan Edelman, UK general manager,
OL,11,Fmerchant services at American Express,
OL,12,Fsaid: "Social media has become the new
OL,13,Fshop window for Britain's high streets.
OL,15,F"What starts as a scroll on social is
OL,16,Fincreasingly translating into real-
OL,17,Fworld visits, increased spending and
OL,18,Fgrowth opportunity for businesses
OL,19,Facross the UK.
OL,26,@tD@GOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782181080
OL,3,CShoppers 'making 1.7bn high street
OL,4,Cvisits per year driven by social media'
OL,6,F"What's striking is that the impact
OL,7,Fdoesn't stop at the venue that first
OL,8,Fcaught a consumer's attention ` social
OL,9,Fmedia is creating a domino effect that
OL,10,Fbenefits neighbouring businesses and
OL,11,Fhelps entire high streets thrive.
OL,13,F"For merchants, particularly those
OL,14,Flooking to attract younger consumers,
OL,15,Fthe ability to turn online hype into
OL,16,Fmemorable in-person experiences has
OL,17,Fnever been more important."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
