OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782181080
OL,3,CShoppers 'making 1.7bn high street
OL,4,Cvisits per year driven by social media'
OL,6,FJarrod Burke, founder of Randalls UK,
OL,7,Fa family-run sweet shop in the East
OL,8,FMidlands, told how an online video had
OL,9,Fa big impact.
OL,11,FHe said: "What's been amazing is
OL,12,Fseeing the impact spread beyond our
OL,13,Fbusiness too ` people are making a day
OL,14,Fof it in Market Harborough, visiting
OL,15,Fother independent shops, cafes and
OL,16,Fbusinesses nearby."
OL,26,@sD@JOUxD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
