OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782181080
OL,3,CShoppers 'making 1.7bn high street
OL,4,Cvisits per year driven by social media'
OL,6,FRichard Lim, chief executive at Retail
OL,7,FEconomics, said: "Social media is not
OL,8,Fjust driving online sales, it is now
OL,9,Falso influencing in-person spend on
OL,10,Fthe UK high street.
OL,12,F"The channel's growth underlines just
OL,13,Fhow quickly shopping via social has
OL,14,Fbecome mainstream, as well as the
OL,15,Fextent of its positive contribution to
OL,16,Fthe long-term health of UK high
OL,17,Fstreets.
OL,26,@oD@ROUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
