PN,30711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782181080
OL,3,CShoppers 'making 1.7bn high street
OL,4,Cvisits per year driven by social media'
OL,6,F"Social media is becoming an
OL,7,Fincreasingly important driver of
OL,8,Ffootfall in its own right, helping
OL,9,Fturn shops, restaurants and venues
OL,10,Finto destinations consumers actively
OL,11,Fseek out, visit and share with others."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@gO]
